endsWiths.description: A list of values that includes events that match the last few characters of the event record field specified as the value of `field`.

equals.description: A list of values that includes events that match the exact value of the event record field specified as the value of `field`. This is the only valid operator that you can use with the `readOnly`, `eventCategory`, and `resources.type` fields.

field.description: Field in an event record on which to filter events to be logged. You can specify only the following values: `readOnly`, `eventSource`, `eventName`, `eventCategory`, `resources.type`, `resources.ARN`.

notEndsWiths.description: A list of values that excludes events that match the last few characters of the event record field specified as the value of `field`.

notEquals.description: A list of values that excludes events that match the exact value of the event record field specified as the value of `field`.

notStartsWiths.description: A list of values that excludes events that match the first few characters of the event record field specified as the value of `field`.

startsWiths.description: A list of values that includes events that match the first few characters of the event record field specified as the value of `field`.
